作者gordonhank (格瑞拉)看板LifeSci_Work標題[試題] 96下 張震東 生物化學甲下 1st期中考時間Tue Apr  8 00:14:51 2008
※ [本文轉錄自 NTU-Exam 看板]

作者: gordonhank (格瑞拉) 看板: NTU-Exam
標題: [試題] 96下生物化學甲下  第一次期中考 張震東教授
時間: Tue Apr  8 00:06:57 2008

課程名稱︰生物化學甲下
課程性質︰必修
課程教師︰張震東教授
開課學院：生物資源暨農學院
開課系所︰生物化學研究所ꤊ考試日期（年月日）︰2008.4.7
考試時限（分鐘）：120 分鐘
是否需發放獎勵金：是
（如未明確表示，則不予發放）

試題 :不一定按照題號
1.What are the five general types of membrane lipids? (5%)
2.Please give the structure of phosphotidylinositol 4,5-bisphophate (5%) and
  the sites of action by phospholipase A1, A2, C and D. (5%)
3.Please describe the asymmetric distribution of phospholipids between the
  inner (cytoplasmic) and outer (extracellular or exoplasmic) monolayers of the
  erythrocyte plasma membrane. (5%)
4.調控ACC的機制(10%)
5.必需脂肪酸為何是必須脂肪酸？(10%)
6.Please describe the cellular pathway leading to increased glucose uptake
  in skeletal muscle after meal. (5%)
7.Describe how V-type ATPases are important for the infection of the
  influenza virus? (10%)
8.Discuss why ketone bodies are excessively form in untreated diabetes. (10%)
9.寫出Oubain的作用。(5%)
10.lovastatin的作用(5%)
11.維他命K和breeding order的影響。(10%)
12.維他命B12作Cofacr的反應。(10%)
13.Describe the reverse cholesterol transport by HDL. (10%)
14.Monoxygenase P-450的作用機制和電子傳遞過程。(10%)
15.Beta oxidation在mitochondria和peroxisome的不同。(5%)
16.寫出各種apolipoprotein的function.(10%)
17.ER對於lipid代謝上的功用。(5%)

